# Performance Optimization Rules

## Compose Optimization
- Use `remember`/`derivedStateOf` appropriately
- Minimize `LaunchedEffect` scope (see [coroutine-rules.mdc](mdc:.cursor/rules/coroutine-rules.mdc) for proper usage)
- Prevent unnecessary recompositions
- Optimize key usage
- Use `LazyColumn` and `LazyRow` for lists

## Memory Management
- Cache image resources
- Prevent memory leaks
- Manage background tasks (use proper coroutine scopes, see [coroutine-rules.mdc](mdc:.cursor/rules/coroutine-rules.mdc))
- Implement pagination for large datasets

## Network Optimization
- Image compression and caching
- Cache API responses
- Use batch requests
- Implement offline-first strategy (for walking sessions, see [sync-strategy-rules.mdc](mdc:.cursor/rules/sync-strategy-rules.mdc))

## App Launch Optimization
- Minimize cold start time
- Implement lazy initialization
- Process heavy tasks in background (use `Dispatchers.IO`, see [coroutine-rules.mdc](mdc:.cursor/rules/coroutine-rules.mdc))
- Optimize screen transitions










